  | 'square'
  | 'square_hd'
  | 'landscape_16_9'
  | 'landscape_4_3'
  | 'portrait_16_9'
  | 'portrait_4_3'
  | {
      width: number;
      height: number;
    };
```

### 4.7 src/fal-image-model.test.ts (Test Pattern)

Tests cover:
- Basic image generation with parameters
- Size and aspect ratio conversion
- Provider options (camelCase & deprecated snake_case)
- Header handling
- Image editing with files
- Mask/inpainting support
- API error handling
- Response metadata
- Binary image download

